paragraphs.text:
run(sql="
with cte as ( 
select distinct a.audienceId, 
                a.email, 
                a.phone,
                a.advId,
                case when a.advId is not null then c.guid
                     when a.advId is null and a.email is not null then b.guid 
                end as guid_1
from `temp.adv` a 
left join `last300Days(saleOrder)` b
on a.email=b.email
left join `last300Days(appHeartBeat)` c
on a.advId=c.advId)

select count(distinct guid_1) from cte
",1000)

run(sql="
with cte as ( 
select distinct a.audienceId, 
                a.email, 
                a.phone,
                a.advId,
                case when a.advId is not null then c.guid
                     when a.advId is null and a.email is not null then b.guid 
                end as guid_1
from `temp.adv` a 
left join `last300Days(saleOrder)` b
on a.email=b.email
left join `last300Days(appHeartBeat)` c
on a.advId=c.advId)

select distinct cte.guid_1, 
                count(a.subOrderId)/7 as SD_ADS, 
                count(distinct case when lower(a.Channel) like '%fb%' then a.subOrderId end)/7 as FB_ADS
from cte 
left join `temp.final_attri2` a 
on cte.guid_1=a.guid
where a.orderDate>='2023-06-12' and a.orderDate<='2023-06-19'
",1000)
